              <div class="views-field views-field-title">
               <h3 class="field-content">
                <a href="/story/march-22-isss-chinas-cities-project-capstone-lecture-features-core-eap-faculty-collaborative">
                 March 22 ISS's China's Cities Project: Capstone Lecture features core EAP faculty collaborative research
                </a>
               </h3>
              </div>
              <div class="views-field views-field-body">
               <div class="field-content">
                <p>
                 On March 22, core East Asia Program faculty who have been collaboratively researching China's urban development will present the ISS China Cities and Plans capstone lecture. 12:30-1:30 in the ILR Conference Center, Room 225.
                </p>
