              <div class="views-field views-field-title">
               <h3 class="field-content">
                <a href="/story/new-initiative-eap-contemporary-japanese-thought">
                 New initiative at EAP: Contemporary Japanese Thought
                </a>
               </h3>
              </div>
              <div class="views-field views-field-body">
               <div class="field-content">
                <p>
                 Building on the strong tradition of intellectual history in Cornell’s Japanese studies, the East Asia Program is developing a new initiative on contemporary Japanese thought that intends to return attention to the place of Japan in our contemporary world.
                </p>
