              <div class="views-field views-field-title">
               <h3 class="field-content">
                <a href="https://caps.cornell.edu/derek-maseloff-combining-china-knowledge-musical-passion">
                 CAPS' alumni Derek Maseloff combining China knowledge and musical passio
                </a>
               </h3>
              </div>
              <div class="views-field views-field-body">
               <div class="field-content">
                <p>
                 Congratulations to China Asia Pacific Studies (CAPS) alumni Derek Maseloff '17, who recently accepted a job with the National Youth Orchestra (NYO) of China as the Director of Artist Partnerships!  In August, he will begin this new chapter of his career by accompanying NYO's 2019 European Tour, after which he will move to NYO-China's headquarters in New York City.  Learn more about NYO-China at
                 <a href="https://nyochina.org/">
                  https://nyochina.org/
                 </a>
                 .  Derek previously worked with NYO-China the summer after his graduation as a resident advisor for their tour across China.
                </p>
               </div>
              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
